  "short_description": "Don't let the mold take over the kitchen and turn all fresh food into rotten zombies. Immerse yourself in tactical roguelite adventures: lead culinary heroes, fight off zombies. Upgrade your fighters with fresh ingredients. Discover new recipes while exploring the mysterious abandoned kitchen.",
